Description:
  Output of bindgen tool on Android rpcbinder headers

  This directory contains a checked in copy of bindgen's output on the rpcbinder
  library. Fuchsia does not have support for running bindgen as part of the build
  process. https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/native/+/refs/heads/main/libs/binder/rust/rpcbinder/BinderBindings.hpp
